in Church</a>, and 23 <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eastern_Catholic_Churches" title="Eastern Catholic Churches">Eastern Catholic Churches</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="white-space: nowrap;"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Catholic_dioceses_(structured_view)" title="List of Catholic dioceses (structured view)">Dioceses</a></th><td><div class="plainlist">
